snippet.textDisplay:
Zeb Is Back!!! YESSS!🎉
I'm just glad I discovered Noorima before I knew she was going to be in CS Pakistan.. 
Another amazing vocalist/performer added to Pakistani music scene... 
Watching the new budding singers with long time stars makes me sigh in relief that there's room for us to grow and we can be introduced to unbelievable fresh talent still!
Xulfi bhai much respect for keep on discovering amazing talents and unveiling them to the world in such a beautiful manner! ❤
